{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-017","title":"Sentence 17","sectionId":"sentences-011","sectionTitle":"Sentence 11-20","pageStart":125,"pageEnd":129,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":31,"duplicateEntryCount":1,"pages":[{"number":125,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 17"},{"type":"text","text":"With modern offices becoming more mechanized, designers are"},{"type":"text","text":"attempting to personalize them with warmer, less severe interiors."},{"type":"text","text":"随着现代办公室变得越来越呆板，设计师们正尝试利用更加温"},{"type":"text","text":"暖而不过于简朴的内部装饰来使办公室个性化。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句主干是Designers are attempting to personalize them。句首是with"},{"type":"text","text":"引导的伴随状态。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"mechanized /ˈmekənaɪzd/ a. 机械化的；呆板的","headword":"mechanized"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 mechanize vt. 使机械化"},{"type":"text","text":"mechanization n. 机械化"},{"type":"entry","text":"attempt /əˈtempt/ vi. 尝试；努力 n. 企图","headword":"attempt"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 strive vi. 努力"},{"type":"entry","text":"personalize /ˈpɜːrsənəlaɪz/ vt. 为个人特制；使个性化","headword":"personalize"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 personalized a. 个性化的"},{"type":"entry","text":"severe /sɪˈvɪr/ a. 过于简朴的，不加装饰的","headword":"severe"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 severity n. 朴素"},{"type":"entry","text":"interior /ɪnˈtɪriər/ n. 内部 a. 内部的；内地的","headword":"interior"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 interior decoration 室内装潢"}]},{"number":126,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"反义 exterior n. 外部a. 外部的"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“装修”有关的词："},{"type":"text","text":"background wall 背景墙"},{"type":"text","text":"bay window （凸出墙外的）凸窗，飘窗"},{"type":"entry","text":"brick /brɪk/ n. 砖","headword":"brick"},{"type":"entry","text":"ceiling /ˈsiːlɪŋ/ n. 天花板","headword":"ceiling"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 ceiling lamp吊灯"},{"type":"entry","text":"cement /sɪˈment/ n. 水泥","headword":"cement"},{"type":"text","text":